id: The partnerships module contains ontologies that define concepts relating to types of partnerships, including incorporated and non-incorporated organizations. Partnerships are defined without reference to jurisdiction-specific legal forms. The abstractions distinguish between types of partnerships and related formation characteristics, as well as kinds of partners and types of partnership equity.
